message:
Dear Geeks

‏Need your help in this survey for my MBA research, the survey is about the factors influencing the customers’ satisfaction in online shopping in Egypt, will be grateful if you can take 5 min. to fill it and share with your friends

‏Edit: The survey is about your last shopping experience, the site meant in the questions is the latest site you performed an online purchase transaction on.

Thank you
story: Mohamed Zaki shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Customers' Satisfaction in Online Retail Shopping
caption: docs.google.com
description: We are conducting a research project concerning online retail shopping, your opinion will be very helpful to us. We assure you the survey data are only for academic research and will not be used for any commercial purposes. If you have online shopping experience, please read the following questions…

data.message:
- I feel secure giving our credit card information at this site.	
- The website has adequate security features	
- I feel I can trust this website	
- I feel safe in my transactions with this website

إيه الفرق بين الأسئلة دي؟

"I feel happy when I use the website"
